sub_title: Global Partner Development Manager - AI Informatics at Philips
summary:
I am a very determined person, I face life and work’s challenges with positivity, passion and enthusiasm. My curiosity, my dynamism and the values I believe in, i.e. improving people's health and well-being through meaningful innovation, are the basis of my great learning motivation and my continuous research.

I am a happy mother, I have to thank my daughter Elide and my son Emanuele who have refined some of my soft skills, such as time management, planning and creativity in solving problems. My life philosophy is:

“Be a good ancestor, plant trees you’ll never see” [Cit. Maori Proverb]

I have a proactive mindset, I can organize my work independently, define objectives and respect deadlines with precision and punctuality. I am satisfied with the achievements I’ve reached, open to changes and new opportunities, always with a view to professional and personal growth.

I am passionate about Healthcare, Innovation, Medical Imaging, Science, Robotics, Artificial Intelligence and Business Management. My mission is to help people to have a better and healthier life.
